Ulanmoqchi bo'lgan serverga kiriladi, login parol bilan.
ssh generatsiya qilinadi.

-C Bu koment shu bilan generatsiya qilganda 
misol: user@62paynet

id_rsa.pub keyni orqaliga shu komentni qo'shadi. Bu qaysi serverligini bilish uchun

   ssh-keygen -C user@62paynet

id_rsa  id_rsa.pub keylar paydo bo'ladi. id_rsa.pub ni authorized_keys ga tashaladi

cat id_rsa.pub > authorized_keys

Keyin id_rsa ni olib qaysi klient hostdan ulanmoqchi bo'lsa ushanga tashalash kerak.

Klient hostga kirib qandaydur nom bilan misol: 62paynet-key.pem file yaratiladi va id_rsa unga tashaladi.
Keyni bu keyni defaultga qo'shib qo'yish kerak

sudo nano ~/.ssh/config

   Host myserver
    HostName 172.24.11.25
    User user
    Port 22
    IdentityFile /srv/sshkey/62paynet-linux.pem


sudo chmod 400 /srv/sshkey/62paynet-linux.pem
sudo chown user:user /srv/sshkey/62paynet-linux.pem

keyin serverga ulanamiz

ssh myserver

Serverda ssh default portni o'zgartirish

sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config

portni # dan chiqarish kerak

Port 46579

save qilib 

sudo systemctl daemon-reexec
sudo systemctl restart ssh
sudo systemctl status ssh
